originalText.text: I was searching for a doctor and 2 people recommended this doctor. This was a good choice. Everything was great, had all my appointments booked for my convenience, my labs were always taken according to schedule, the delivery was very smooth despite all my fears and anxiety. Dr. Shulina promised me that the delivery will be a good experience and so it was. Definitely recommend her to everyone. Thank you

originalText.text: Choosing Dr. Shulina as my doctor through my first pregnancy was definitely one of the best decisions I ever ever made. She is very authentic, concise, makes you feel comfortable through the entire process, and thorough with all of her information. I’m so happy she is my doctor and you will be too!!!

originalText.text: After being in the wrong hands for my first pregnancy (which was during the height of COVID), I knew from day one that I was in the right hands this time with Dr Shulina for my second pregnancy. She gets to know every patient personally and makes you feel cared for and understood. I highly recommend her. All of the staff are friendly and helpful.

originalText.text: Dr. Shulina is the best OB and overall doctor in NYC. She takes the time to explain everything that is happening under her care and is incredibly knowledgeable. Dr. Rhee, Rachel, and Leslie at the practice are all also very excellent so you can have confidence that no matter who is on call that you will receive the best care. I am so grateful to have gone through my pregnancy journey with this amazing practice. 5 stars aren’t enough to represent Dr. Shulina’s excellent care!
